info.author: John Mulligan
info.description:
Last.fm/Audioscrobbler, a social music site,
        has a number of webservices. This module provides a easy to use
        (in the authors opinion) python programming interface to the
        XML feeds they provide.
        (Special Thanks: Mark Woodson, Matt Chisholm)
info.name: scrob-web-services
info.summary: A python programming interface for last.fm/audioscobbler
